data.description: Great opportunity to own nice 2 Bedroom Home with a 1 car Garage. Kitchen and Living room have vaulted ceiling with an open concept. Kitchen has updated Kitchen Cabinets with Granite counter tops. Home also has a nice size fenced in yard as well. Walking distance to Lake St. George Elementary. Easy access to curlew and Tampa Rd. Less than 10 minutes to Honeymoon Island. Plenty of shopping and great Restaurants.
